Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:02.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(434,465)\fad(0,700)\fsp2\fnarial\fs24\fscy55\b0}t x s u b
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:12.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's five centimeters per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,秒速5センチなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:16.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ　何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:21.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,桜の花の落ちるスピード 秒速5センチメートル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The speed at which cherry blossoms fall.\NIt's five centimeters per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふうん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure know a lot of stuff like that, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:25.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリ　そういうこと\Nよく知ってるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:26.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふふん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... don't you think it kinda looks like snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:31.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ　なんだか　まるで\N雪みたいじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すうかなー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.07,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハァ　ハァ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:36.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:39.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,待ってよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Takaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:46.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:53.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来年も一緒に桜　見れるといいね！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if we could watch the cherry\Nblossoms fall again together next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:11.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野タカキさまへ　たいへんご無沙汰しております
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"To Thono Takaki-sama. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's been a really long time. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:18.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらの夏も暑いけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"Summer's pretty hot around here,\Nbut compared to Tokyo, it's so much milder. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:22.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東京に比べれば　ずっと過ごしやすいです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:27.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも今にして思えば\N私は東京のあのムシ暑い夏も好きでした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"But when I think about it,\NI liked Tokyo's hot, humid summers, too. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:32.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,溶けてしまいそうに熱いアスファルトも\N陽炎のむこうの高層ビルも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"The melting-hot asphalt,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"the distant skyscrapers, shimmering in the heat,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"and the freezing air-conditioning\Nin department stores and on subways. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:36.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,デパートや地下鉄の寒いくらいの冷房も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"The last time we were together was at\Nour elementary school graduation. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:41.55,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私たちが最後に会ったのは\N小学校の卒業式でしたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.54,0:01:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's already been half a year since. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれからもう半年です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"So, Takaki-kun... "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ　タカキくん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"... do you still remember me?."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のこと　覚えていますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.55,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,前略　タカキくんへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Takaki-kun... "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:59.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お返事ありがとう　嬉しかったです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thanks for replying. "
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"It made me so happy. "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:05.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もうすっかり秋ですね\Nこちらは紅葉がキレイです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's already well into autumn and the\Nleaves are turning beautiful colors. "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"I had to pull out a sweater the day before\Nyesterday for the first time this year. "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.30,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今年　最初のセーターをおととい私は出しました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.14,0:02:11.07,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くん!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何？アブレター？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違いますよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for having asked you to do all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんね　全部お願いしちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:18.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ　すぐ終わりましたから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, I finished quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.08,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう　ねっ　転校しちゃうってホント？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. So, is it true\Nthat you'll be transferring schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:23.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ　はい　3学期いっぱいです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, at the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagoshima. Because of my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.62,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿児島です　親の都合で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:28.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうかー　寂しくなるなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... it'll be lonely around here without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:34.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最近は部活で朝が早いので\N今　この手紙は電車で書いています
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm actually writing this letter on the train because\Npractice has been starting really early lately. "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この前　髪を切りました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"I had my hair cut the other day. "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's so short you can even see my ears... "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,耳が出るくらい短くしちゃったから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もし会っても\N私って分からないかもしれませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"... so you probably wouldn't even recognize me\Nif you saw me. "
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいまー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:45.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おかえり
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:59.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくんも　きっと少しずつ\N変わっていくのでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"I bet you're changing little\Nby little too, Takaki-kun. "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Takaki-kun... "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:18.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,拝啓　寒い日が続きますがお元気ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Have you been doing well during these cold days?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こちらは　もう何度か雪が降りました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's already snowed a number of times here. "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:30.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私はそのたびにものすごい重装備で\N学校にツ通っています
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Every time it does, I wrap myself\Nin layers of clothes when I go to school. "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東京は雪はまだだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"It hasn't snowed in Tokyo yet, right?."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Even though I moved away... "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,引越してきてからも\Nついクセで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東京のぶんの天気予報まで見てしまいます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"... I still look at Tokyo's\Nweather forecast out of habit. "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.30,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハァ　ハァ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,雨でも降らねえかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish it would rain one of these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも居内でもキツイぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be any better indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なぁ　栃木って行ったことあるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... have you guys ever been to Tochigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:52.31,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハァ？どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tochigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,栃木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうやって行くのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how you get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さぁ...新幹線とか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A bullet train or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠いよな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:03.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一年！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Freshmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Onto the final three laps! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:06.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ラスト三周！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ファイト！オーッ！\Nファイト！オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:13.19,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今度はタカキくんの転校が\N決まったということ驚きました
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was surprised to hear that you were\Nthe one transferring schools this time. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:17.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お互いに昔から転校には\N慣れているわけですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"We both got used to transferring schools\Nwhen we were little.. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それにしても鹿児島だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"But still... Kagoshima.\NThat's kind of far away, isn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,％今度はちょっと遠いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いざという時に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's no longer a distance where I can just\Njump on a train and see you whenever I want... "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:28.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,電車に乗って会いに行けるような\N距離ではなくなってしまうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"So... I guess... that makes me feel a little lonely. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱり...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:31.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,少し...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと寂しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:38.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうか　どうか\Nタカキくんが元気でいますように
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please be well, Takaki-kun. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,前略　タカキくんへ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Takaki-kun... "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:59.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,3月4日の約束　とても嬉しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm so happy we'll see each other on March 4th. "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,会うのは　もう一年ぶりですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"It'll be just about a year\Nsince we last met, won't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"For some reason, I feel kind of nervous. "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:05.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだか緊張してしまいます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うちの近くに大きな桜の樹があって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's a really large cherry tree close to\Nmy house, so I bet that in the spring... "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,春には　そこでもたぶん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:21.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,花びらが秒速5センチで地上に降っています
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"... the petals will fall\Nat five centimeters per second. "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくんと一緒に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm really hoping the spring\Nwill come with you that day, Takaki-kun. "
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:29.07,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,春もやってきてくれればいいのにって思います
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna stop somewhere on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it's raining out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The forecast said it's supposed\Nto turn to snow by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:52.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,予報では夕方から雪になるって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I thought it felt cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え～っ　寒いと思ったよ\Nもう3月なのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're already in March...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,風邪引きそうだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it feels like I'm gonna catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねっ　あったかいもの\N飲んでこうよ　下北で降りてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get off at Shimokita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:01.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.53,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno, let's get to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,部活行こうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:06.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのさ　俺\N今日ちょっと部活ダメなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,About that... I don't think I can make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,引越しの準備か？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting ready to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなトコ　悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:18.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の駅まで来てくれるのはとても\N助かるのですけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm glad you're coming all the way out\Nto the station closest to me... "
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:21.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠いので\Nどうか気をつけてきて下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"... but it's a long trip, so please be careful. "
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:26.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,約束の夜7時に駅の待合室で待っています
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll be waiting for you in the station's\Nwaiting room at 7:00 that night. "
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:50.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリとの約束の当日は昼すぎから雪になった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the day Akari and I were to meet,\Nthe rain turned to snow in the afternoon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:55.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ　ねえタカキくん！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねこ！チョビだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that cat, Chobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こいつ　いつもここにいるね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always lying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも今日は１人みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks like he's all by himself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:05.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ミミは　どうしたの？\N１人じゃ寂しいよねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your friend Mimi?\NIt must be lonely all by yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハァ　ハァ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの本　どう？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that book so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか\N昨日一晩で40億年分読んじゃった！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night I read four billion years' worth of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どのあたり？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you at now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:24.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アノマロカリスが出てくるあたり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about when the Anomalocaris start showing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カンブリア紀！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cambrian era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like the Hallucigenia. They look like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:30.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私　ハルキゲニアが好きだな　こんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:31.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ　似てるかも
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくんは何のファン？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you like, Takaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:34.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,オパビニアかな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Opabinia, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:37.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あー　眼が5つあるヒトだよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The five-eyed one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:42.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕とアカリは\N精神的にどこかよく似ていたと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think Akari and I were a lot alike somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exactly one year after I transferred to Tokyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕が東京に転校してきた１年後にー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A new friend just transferred to our school.\NThis is Tohno Takaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリが同じクラスに転校してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Akari transferred into my class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting today, Shinohara Akari-san\Nwill be joining our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:53.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ体が小さく病気がちだった僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because our bodies were still small,\Nfrail, and prone to illness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the two of us preferred the library\Nover playing on the sportsfield.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,グランドよりは図書館が好きで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.15,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから僕たちはごく自然に仲良くなり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naturally, we became friends...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのせいでクラスメイトから\Nからかわれることもあったけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and because of that, there were times when\Nour classmates would tease us. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:03.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもー
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:11.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お互いがいれば不思議にそういうことは\Nあまり怖くはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as we were both together,\Nstrangely, things like that didn't scare us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, what a nice guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕たちは　いずれ同じ中学に通い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet, for some reason, I thought we'd\Nend up going to the same middle school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and stay together, just as we were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この先もずっと一緒にだと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:24.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしてだとう　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...from that point on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinjuku, Shinjuku, last stop. For passengers which...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.15,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿　新宿　終点です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お振りのお客様は...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ＪＲ線　京王線\N地下鉄はお乗り換えです...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...JR Line, Heiou Line, subway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:44.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿駅に1人で来たのは初めてで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the first time I'd gone\Nto Shinjuku Station alone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これから乗る路線も僕にはすべて初めてだった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and all the lines I would soon be riding\Nwould also be firsts for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハァ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.15,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ドキドキしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart was pounding.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これから　僕は　アカリに会うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was going to see Akari again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この前の子　どうだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.53,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:14.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら　西商の！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that Nisshou boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え～？趣味悪くない？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? His tastes were a little gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be arriving at Musashi-Urawa shortly.\NAgain, this is Musashi-Urawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At our next stop, Musashi-Urawa,\Nin order to connect with the express train...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:27.71,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,...快速列車\N待ち合わせのためこの列車は４分ほど停車します
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to connect with the express train,\Nthis train will be stopping for 4 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Those passengers who wish to quickly reach Yonohonmachi\Nand Oomiya please board...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:31.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,与野本町\N大宮までお急ぎの方は向かいの...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの...篠原と申しますけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... this is Shinohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの　タカキくんいらっしゃいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, is Takaki-kun there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリちゃんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Akari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え...転校？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're transferring schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:10.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,西中はどうすんだ？せっかく受かったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nishi Middle School?\NYou went through all that trouble to get accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:14.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,栃木の公立に手続きするって...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'd handle the paperwork of transferring\Nme to the public school in Tochigi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:19.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや...アカリが謝ることないけで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No... there's no reason to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:23.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,葛飾の叔母さんちから　通いたいって言ったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them I still wanted to go\Nfrom my aunt's house in Katsushika, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...they said I couldn't until I was older.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:27.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと大きくなってからじゃないとダメだって...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,わかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand... you don't have to say anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:30.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もういいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,耳が痛くなるくらい　押しあてた受話器ごしに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through the receiver painfully pressed\Nagainst my ear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:46.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリが傷つくのが手にとるように分かった　でも...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Akari's own pain was palpable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... there was nothing I could do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:01.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,乗り換えのターミナル駅は帰宅を\N始めた人々で混み合っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The terminal I transferred at\Nwas crowded with people heading home...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.63,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰の靴も雪の水を吸ってぐっしょり濡れていて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and everyone's shoes were soaked from the snow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,空気はー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The frigid air was saturated with the classic smell\Nof a snowy city day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:10.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,雪の日の都市　独特の匂いに満ちて冷たかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お客様にお知らせいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All passengers, your attention please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇都宮線　小山　宇都宮方面行き列車は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the snowy weather conditions, the Utsunomiya Line\Noutbound trains traveling to Oomiya and Utsunomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:19.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいま雪のため　到着が８分ほど遅れております
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be experiencing an 8 minute delay in arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところお客様には\N大変ご迷惑おかけいたしますが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for any inconvenience in your busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:26.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その瞬間まで　僕は電車が遅れるなんていう可能性を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Until that moment, I hadn't even considered\Nthe possibility of one of my trains being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,考えもしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,不安が急に大きくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My creeping anxiety suddenly became much greater.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:40.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいまこの電車は雪のため\N１０分ほど遅れて運行しております
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This train is currently running 10 minutes late\Ndue to the snowy weather conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:44.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところ列車遅れておりますこと　お詫びいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for any inconvenience in your busy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大宮駅を過ぎてしばらくすると
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After we had passed a little beyond Oomiya Station...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...almost all the passing buildings\Nsuddenly vanished from view.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:54.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,風景からはあっという間に建物が少なくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Next stop is Kuki. Kuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:08.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,次は久喜　久喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:13.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,到着が大変遅れましたこと\Nお詫び申し上げます
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for our terribly late arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:19.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東武伊勢崎線にお乗り換えの方は\N５番出口におまわり下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those passengers transferring to the Tobu Isesaki Line,\Nplease make your way around to Exit #5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,後続列車が遅れているため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the next train's delay, this train will be stopping\Nat this station for the next 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:26.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この列車は到駅にて１０分ほど停車します
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところ大変ご迷惑おかけいたしますが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for any inconvenience in your busy day,\Nand appreciate your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:32.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今しばらくお待ち下さいますよう\Nお願いいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,後続列車が遅れているため
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the next train's delay, this train will be stopping\Nat this station for the next 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この列車は到駅にて１０分ほど停車します
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for any inconvenience in your busy day, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところ大変ご迷惑を\Nおかけいたしますが...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,野木　野木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Nogi. Nogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お客様にお断りとお詫び申し上げます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,To all passengers, we express our deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the continuing delay of the following train, this train will\Nbe stopping at this station for an extended period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:16.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,後続列車遅延のため\Nこの列車は当駅でしばらくの間停車します
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところ大変ご迷惑...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for any inconvenience in your busy day,\Nand appreciate your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:22.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,駅と駅との間は信じられないくらい\N離れていて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:27.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,電車は一駅ごとに\N信じられないくらい長い間 停車した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.39,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and the train would stop for an unbelievably\Nlong amount of time at each station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurihashi > Koga > Nogi > Mamada > Oyama
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Omoigawa > Tochigi > Ohirashita > Iwafune > Sano
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,窓の外の見たこともないような雪に荒野も
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wilderness on the other side of the\Nwindow seemed like nothing I'd ever experienced before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:56.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じわじわと流れていく時間も\N痛いような空腹も
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The slowly ticking time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and my pangs of hunger...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕をますます心細くさせていった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...continued to dampen my spirits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:03.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,約束の時間を過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time we had planned to meet had passed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:08.62,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今頃アカリは\Nきっと不安になり始めていると思う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...so I had the feeling that Akari was beginning to worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.40,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの日...あの電話の日ー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the day she called...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:20.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕よりもずっと大きな不安を\N抱えているはずのアカリに対して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Akari must've been so much more jittery and upset than me,\Nyet I couldn't find the words to console her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:24.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,優しい言葉をかけることのできなかった自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひどく　恥ずかしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt so ashamed of myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As we look back, we thank our teachers\Nfor all they've done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:32.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あおげば尊し...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:34.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日でショナラだね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess after today... this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Any summer vacation plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:44.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリからの最初の手紙が\N届いたのはそれから半年後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I received the first letter from Akari\Nhalf a year later...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,中１の夏だった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...during the summer of my first year of middle school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I remember every last word of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:51.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼女からの文面はすべて覚えた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over the two weeks before the day we were to meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:53.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,約束の今日まで２週間かけて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I spent my time writing a letter I would give her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕はアカリに渡すための手紙を書いた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was filled with all the things I had to tell her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:01.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリに伝えなければいけないこと\N聞いて欲しいことが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the things I wanted her to hear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There were so many.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当に　僕にはたくさんあった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:09.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大変お待たせいたしました\Nまもなく宇都宮行き発車いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize terribly for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This train will shortly begin\Nits departure towards Utsunomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Oyama. Oyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:24.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,小山　小山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For those passengers changing over to the\NTohoku Bullet Train, please transfer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:27.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東北新幹線ご利用の方は\Nお乗り換えです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Those passengers transferring to the down-train,\Nthe Tohoku Bullet Train towards Morioka, please transfer to Line 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東北新幹線下り盛岡方面\Nお乗り換えの方は１番線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those passengers transferring to the up-train\Ntowards Tokyo, please transfer to Line 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:37.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,上り東京方面お乗り換えの方は\N５番線へおまわり下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Those passengers transferring to the Mito Line-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お客様にお知らせいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to snowy weather conditions, the\NRyomo Line is currently experiencing a serious delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:46.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいま両毛線は雪のため\N大幅な遅れをもって運転しております
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お客様には大変ご迷惑をおかけいたしております
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for the terrible inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,列車到着まで今しばらくお待ち下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask that you please be patient and wait\Na little longer until the train arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The next up-train headed for-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.62,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.74,0:16:01.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリの待つ駅に向かうしかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I had no choice but to keep going towards\Nthe station where Akari was waiting.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the up-train, Line 8, towards Takasaki,\Npassing Ashikaga and Maebashi on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:17:00.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,８番線\N足利.前橋方面高崎行き上り電車が参ります
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:03.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,白線の内側に下がって...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand behind the white line-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All passengers, your attention please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:36.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お客様にご案内いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:41.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいま降雪によるダイヤの乱れのため\N少々停車いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the disrupted schedule from the heavy snowfall\Nthis train will be making a temporary stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:44.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところ大変　恐縮ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize terribly for this inconvenience in your busy day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,現在のところ復旧の目処は\N立っておりません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...but presently, we are unable to resume normal service.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,繰り返します
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:53.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただいま降雪によるダイヤの乱れのため\N少々停車いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お急ぎのところ大変　恐縮ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:59.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,現在のところ復旧の目処は\N立っておりません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Takaki-kun... "
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.03,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくん　お元気ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"How are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm actually writing this letter on the train because\Npractice has been starting really early lately. "
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:10.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,部活で朝が早いので\Nこの手紙は電車で書いています
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every time I tried to picture Akari from her letters...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:16.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手紙から想像するアカリはなぜか\Nいつも１人だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...she was always alone for some reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, the train remained stopped\Nin the barren wilderness for two hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:22.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,電車はそれから結局ー
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:26.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,２時間も何もない荒野に停まり続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each minute felt like an eternity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:30.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たった１分がものすごく長く感じられ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With clear malice towards me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:33.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,時間は　はっきりとした悪意をもって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...time continued to drift slowly forwards around me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕は上をゆっくりと流れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my teeth tightly together...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕は　きつく歯をくいしばり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:44.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただとにかく\N泣かないように耐えているしかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and could do nothing but endure the pain\Nand hold back my tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akari...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please tell me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:50.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうか...もう...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...you've already...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.13,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,家に...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...returned home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰っていてくれればいいのに...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Line 3 towards Takasaki, passing Ashikaga\Nand Maebashi on the way has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:16.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,３番線 足利.前橋方面高崎行き列車\N到着いたします
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the snowy weather conditions, this train\Nwill be making a temporary stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:21.53,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この電車は雪にためしばらく停車します
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハァッ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.16,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウッ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おいしい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:34.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう？普通のほうじ茶だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just hot roasted tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:37.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほうじ茶？初めて飲んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Roasted tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time having it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding. I'm sure you've had it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ウソ　ぜったい　飲んだことあるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:40.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:48.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それからこれ...\N私が作ったから味の保証はないんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And... since I made this, I can't really guarantee\Nhow good it'll taste, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よかったら食べて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お腹すいてたんだ　すごく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:20:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:20:59.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:07.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今まで食べたものの中で一番おいしい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most delicious rice ball I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大袈裟だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:09.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ホントだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just because you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとお腹がすいてたからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:12.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:13.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうよ予5占
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も食べよっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll have a bite, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So... you're moving soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:22.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,引越し　もうすぐだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　来週
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagoshima, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿児島かぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:26.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,栃木も遠かったけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Though this trip to Tochigi was pretty far, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:33.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふふ　帰れなくなっちゃったもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even go home today now, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そろそろ閉めますよ もう電車もないですし
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be closing soon.\NThere aren't any more trains coming or going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハイ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:42.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほんな雪ですから　お気をつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home in this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:43.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see the tree way out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,見える？あの樹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.67,0:22:11.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手紙の樹？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the tree from your letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a cherry tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.11,0:22:13.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　桜の樹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:21.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まるで...雪みたいじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't you think it looks a little like snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:45.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その瞬間ー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:50.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠とか心とか魂とかいうものが\Nどこにあるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I felt like I knew where eternity,\Nour hearts and ours souls all lay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:52.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.75,0:22:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt as though we had shared\Nall the experiences of my 13 years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:56.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,13年間　生きてきたことの全てを\N分かちあえたように僕は思い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:59.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それから　次の瞬間ー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then... in the next moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たまらなく...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I was suddenly filled\Nwith an insufferable sadness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:03.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akari's warmth... and her soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:08.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリのその温もりを　その魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,0:23:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could I take them in,\Nand where could I bring them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:12.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どのように扱えばいいのか\Nどこに持っていけばいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt that sad because I didn't have those answers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.77,0:23:15.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが僕には分からなかったからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clearly knew that from that point on,\Nwe wouldn't be together forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:21.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕たちはこの先も\Nずっと一緒にいることはできないと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:23.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はっきりと分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The overwhelming weight of our lives to come...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:27.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕たちの前には　いまだ巨大すぎる人生が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and the uncertainty of time hung over us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:32.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,茫漠とした時間がどうしようもなく\N横たわっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... the creeping anxiety that had taken hold of me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.29,0:23:36.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:41.53,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕を捉えたその不安は\Nやがてゆるやかに溶けていき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...would soon gradually melt away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:46.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あとにはアカリの\N柔らかな唇だけが残っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And all that remained would be\Nthe feeling of Akari's soft lips.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We spent that night in a shack\Nby the side of a field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.22,0:24:05.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その夜ー
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.89,0:24:10.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕たちは畑の脇にあった\N小さな納屋で過ごした
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wrapping ourselves in an old blanket,\Nwe talked on and on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:15.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,古い毛布にくるまり\N長い時間話し続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:17.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつの間にか眠っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...until finally, we had fallen asleep, side by side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:22.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,朝　動き始めた電車に乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next morning, as I boarded the train\Nthat had started its run again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:25.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕はアカリと別れた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.38,0:24:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I parted with Akari..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.61,0:24:29.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.89,0:24:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Takaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:30.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくん...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.32,0:24:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.48,0:24:31.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ん...？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.18,0:24:34.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,タカキくんは...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.43,0:24:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Takaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:38.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとこの先も大丈夫だと思う\Nぜったい！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.91,0:24:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure you'll be okay from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.82,0:24:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.98,0:24:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.46,0:24:42.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリも元気で！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.50,0:24:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, you be well, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.53,0:24:45.19,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手紙書くよ！電話も！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.57,0:24:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.57,0:24:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.68,0:25:01.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,アカリへの手紙をなくしてしまったことを
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.69,0:25:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never told Akari that I'd lost the letter\NI wanted to give her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:03.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕はアカリに言わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.83,0:25:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I felt that my world\Nhad completely changed after that kiss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.88,0:25:08.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのキスの前と後とでは
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.62,0:25:13.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世界の何もかもが\N変わってしまったような気がしたからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.80,0:25:25.33,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼女を守れるだけの力が\N欲しいと強く思った
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.80,0:25:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I wanted was the strength to protect her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.99,0:25:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that thought in my mind, I continued to gaze out\Nover the landscape beyond the window... forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.00,0:25:29.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけを考えながら僕はいつまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.91,0:25:33.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,窓の外の景色を見続けていた
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.87,0:27:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanae, are you going to go after school, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.96,0:27:03.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カナエ　放課後も行くの？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.10,0:27:05.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　お姉ちゃんは平気？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.10,0:27:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, are you okay with that, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.70,0:27:08.33,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいよ　でも勉強もちゃんとやんなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.83,0:27:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me. But be sure to get to your studies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:09.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.97,0:27:40.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふう...よし
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.84,0:27:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.92,0:27:56.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.22,0:27:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.70,0:27:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Tohno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.75,0:27:59.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おはよう　遠野くん　今朝も早いね
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.59,0:27:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really early this morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.93,0:28:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Sumida. You went to the beach again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.99,0:28:02.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田も　海　行ってきたんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.34,0:28:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.59,0:28:04.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,頑張るんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.59,0:28:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're practicing hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.29,0:28:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.43,0:28:08.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなにでも...へへへ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.02,0:28:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Tohno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.06,0:28:10.53,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,またね！遠野くん
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.70,0:28:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.96,0:28:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? It's time to begin making your choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.03,0:28:16.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいかぁ？　そろそろ決める時期だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.78,0:28:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to turn it in by Monday, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.84,0:28:18.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,月曜までに提出だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.02,0:28:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And remember to talk it over with your parents before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.11,0:28:21.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ご家族とよく相談して書いてくるように
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.14,0:28:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Sasaki-san's gonna be going to a college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.78,0:28:26.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,佐々木さん　東京の大学行くみたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.32,0:28:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise there. I was thinking of maybe\Ngoing to a 2-year college in Kumamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.61,0:28:30.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さすが 私の熊本の短大かな～
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.05,0:28:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.28,0:28:31.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カナエは？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.39,0:28:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.55,0:28:33.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え？うーん...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.66,0:28:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.72,0:28:34.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,就職だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.02,0:28:36.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うーん...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.10,0:28:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.48,0:28:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really haven't thought about it at all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.52,0:28:38.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんたホンと何も考えてないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.62,0:28:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing on your mind is Tohno-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.09,0:28:40.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんのことだけね
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.70,0:28:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He definitely left his girlfriend in Tokyo, I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.83,0:28:42.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつゼッタイ　東京に彼女いるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.96,0:28:43.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.11,0:28:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.03,0:28:45.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うっふふふ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.90,0:29:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not going well for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.96,0:29:13.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まだ上手くいかない？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.76,0:29:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... what's gotten into me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.86,0:29:16.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　どうしちゃったのかな...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.81,0:29:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if you don't think about it too much.\NYou'll be able to surf again in no time, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.86,0:29:20.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんまり　悩まない方がいいよ\Nそのうちまた乗れるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.90,0:29:23.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんは気楽でいいわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.97,0:29:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be nice taking things so easy, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.06,0:29:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you in such a rush for?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.34,0:29:25.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なに　焦ってんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.71,0:29:29.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,このままじゃ卒業まで言えないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.75,0:29:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I won't be able to say it before graduation...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.13,0:29:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.33,0:29:50.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがと　お姉ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.85,0:29:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take you home, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.96,0:29:51.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,送ってくわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.96,0:29:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. I'll take my bike home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.10,0:29:54.16,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん　カブで帰る！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.36,0:30:23.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あっ　澄田　今帰り？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.85,0:30:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumida, you're on your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.66,0:30:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.83,0:30:25.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　遠野くんも？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.87,0:30:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Tohno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.87,0:30:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.03,0:30:27.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.19,0:30:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.30,0:30:28.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒に帰らない？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.49,0:30:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I had a tail like a dog's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.50,0:30:32.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もし私に犬みたいな尻尾があったら
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.57,0:30:36.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと嬉しさを隠しきれずに\Nぶんぶんと振ってしまったと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.60,0:30:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I'm sure it'd be wagging back and forth right now,\Nsince I'd be unable to hide my happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.39,0:30:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sort of relieved and thought to myself,\N"Thank goodness I'm not really a dog... "
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.44,0:30:42.31,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　私は犬じゃなくて良かったな～\Nなんてホッとしながら思って
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.48,0:30:46.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうことに我ながらバカだなぁと呆れて
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.49,0:30:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and I was surprised at how foolish I was\Nfor thinking what I did earlier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.38,0:30:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even still, the trip home with Tohno-kun was bliss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.42,0:30:47.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.49,0:30:50.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんとの帰り道は幸せだった
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.59,0:30:59.40,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,最初から遠野くんは他の男の子たちとは\Nどこか少し違っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.72,0:30:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right from the start, Tohno-kun seemed\Na little different from the other boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.47,0:31:01.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野貴樹です
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.51,0:31:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tohno Takaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorta used to transferring schools\Nbecause of my parents' jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.97,0:31:06.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,親の仕事で転校には慣れていますが\Nこの島にはまだ慣れていません
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.58,0:31:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'm not too used to this island yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.77,0:31:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.94,0:31:08.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よろしくお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.26,0:31:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fell in love at first sight on that day in the second year of middle\Nschool, and wanted to go to the same high school as him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:12.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,中2のその日のうちに好きになって\N彼と同じ高校に行きたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.24,0:31:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...so I studied really hard, was somehow accepted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.38,0:31:16.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ものすごく勉強をがんばって\Nなんてか合格して
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.58,0:31:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and every single time I saw him,\Nfell more and more in love with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.68,0:31:21.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでもまだ遠野くんの姿を見るたびに\Nもっと好きになっていってしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.88,0:31:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's so scary, and everyday is painful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.02,0:31:25.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが怖くて　毎日が苦しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet every time I see him, I'm filled with such happiness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.13,0:31:27.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも会えるたびに幸せで
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.38,0:31:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that I'm at a loss for what to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.43,0:31:30.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分でもどうしようもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.89,0:31:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno-kun, there you go buying the same one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.13,0:31:33.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くん　また　同じの
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.93,0:31:36.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふふ　これウマいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.46,0:31:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.27,0:31:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumida, you always think your decisions\Nthrough seriously, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.30,0:31:39.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田は　なんかいつも真剣だよね\Nものすごく
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.57,0:31:40.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.65,0:31:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.82,0:31:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.94,0:31:44.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先行ってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.62,0:31:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.81,0:31:45.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.01,0:31:47.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これ下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.14,0:31:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.25,0:31:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be 90 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.35,0:31:48.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,90円ね
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.14,0:31:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.15,0:31:49.84,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハイ
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.93,0:31:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.95,0:31:51.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも　ありがとね
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.52,0:31:55.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.10,0:32:04.15,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お帰り　何買ったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.14,0:32:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.17,0:32:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.26,0:32:05.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　迷ったんだけど...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.27,0:32:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was hard to pick, but I went with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.67,0:32:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes, Tohno-kun would be writing a text message...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.70,0:32:09.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんは時々\N誰かにメールを打っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.20,0:32:14.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたびに私は　それが\N私あてのメールだったらいいのにって
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and every time he did, I would always wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.53,0:32:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that the text message he was writing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.57,0:32:18.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしても　いつも　思ってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.73,0:32:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...would be addressed to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.55,0:32:24.81,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.99,0:32:27.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ワンワン！ワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.01,0:32:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabu, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.09,0:32:29.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カブ！ただいまー！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.49,0:32:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabu, Kabu!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.69,0:32:32.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カブカブ　帰ってきたよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.97,0:32:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.63,0:32:33.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ワフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.78,0:32:58.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,町役場からお知らせします\N次回の当番スタンドは坂井の農協給油...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.83,0:32:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a message from your town hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.15,0:32:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The next normal open gasoline stand will be at the\NSakai Agricultural Cooperative Gas Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.50,0:33:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumida Kanae-san from Class 3-1...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.59,0:33:01.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,3年1組の澄田花苗さん
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.22,0:33:03.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤先生がお呼びです\N生徒指導室まで来て下さい
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.29,0:33:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...Itou-sensei is calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.86,0:33:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the Guidance Counselor's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.06,0:33:05.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野の彼女じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.71,0:33:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your girlfriend, Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.00,0:33:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.06,0:33:07.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼女とかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.05,0:33:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one in the grade who hasn't filled one out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.16,0:33:13.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,学年で出してないのは澄田だけだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.88,0:33:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.97,0:33:15.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,すみません...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.32,0:33:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this isn't something someone in my position\Nshould be saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.57,0:33:20.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのなぁ　こう言っちゃ何だが\Nそんなに悩むようなことじゃないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.14,0:33:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but this isn't really something\Nyou have to wrack your brain over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.63,0:33:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Sumida-sensei said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.71,0:33:22.83,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田先生は何て言ってるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.82,0:33:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.94,0:33:24.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.61,0:33:25.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ふうっ...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.77,0:33:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really can't decide, then how about\Na 2-year college within the prefecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.88,0:33:30.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしても決められないなら\N県内の短大とかはどうなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.72,0:33:32.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.78,0:33:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.59,0:33:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onee-chan has nothing to do with it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.59,0:33:36.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんは関係ないのに...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.57,0:33:54.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.76,0:33:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.51,0:33:59.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お姉ちゃんにねだって\Nはじめたサーフィンも
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.55,0:33:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...surfing, even after I pestered my sister\Nso much to teach me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.69,0:34:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the most important guy who takes up all of my thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.71,0:34:02.65,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一番大切だと思う　あの人のことも
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.85,0:34:06.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私はまだ　全然...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.92,0:34:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...are two things I'm still no good at.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.21,0:34:33.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつもありがとね
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.24,0:34:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.04,0:34:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. See you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.15,0:34:35.74,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いえ　それじゃあまた
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.04,0:35:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever I go to where Tohno-kun is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.18,0:35:06.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんがいる場所にくると
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.48,0:35:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...deep down, my heart... it clenches up... just a little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.55,0:35:10.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,胸の奥が...少し苦しくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.05,0:35:11.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くん！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.18,0:35:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.19,0:35:15.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田?どうしたの　よく分かったね
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.25,0:35:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumida, what's up? I'm surprised you found me way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.12,0:35:20.15,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,へへへ　遠野くんの単車があったから\N来ちゃった　いい？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.17,0:35:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your bike, so I decided to come on by.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.50,0:35:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.09,0:35:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.26,0:35:22.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　そっか　嬉しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.80,0:35:25.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は単車置き場で会えなかったからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.86,0:35:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't run into each other at the bike shed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.67,0:35:26.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.73,0:35:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.03,0:35:28.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,彼は優しい
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.05,0:35:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's really kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.16,0:35:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So kind that sometimes it feels like I'm going to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.24,0:35:32.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,時々　泣いてしまいそうになる
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.39,0:35:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you going to test to get into college?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.48,0:35:37.44,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ　遠野くんは受験？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.60,0:35:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm going to take a few for some universities in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.71,0:35:40.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　東京の大学受ける
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.58,0:35:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.71,0:35:45.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,東京...そっか　そうだと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.19,0:35:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.83,0:35:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.95,0:35:47.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.99,0:35:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you want to go far away from here, for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.15,0:35:50.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠くに行きたそうだもの\Nなんとなく
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.60,0:35:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Sumida?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.66,0:35:51.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田は？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.93,0:35:52.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,う～ん...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even really know what's going to happen tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.26,0:35:56.63,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私　明日のこともよく分からないのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.61,0:35:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.73,0:35:58.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だぶん　誰だってそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.58,0:36:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You too, Tohno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.67,0:36:00.50,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ワン！遠野くんも？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.55,0:36:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.60,0:36:01.43,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.34,0:36:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like you have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.37,0:36:04.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぜんぜん　迷いなんてないみたいに見える
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.34,0:36:08.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか　迷ってばかりなんだ　俺
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.44,0:36:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop that. I'm filled with nothing but worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.65,0:36:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing all that I can just to keep up.\NI have no breathing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.71,0:36:12.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出来ることをなんとかやってるだけ\N余裕ないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.78,0:36:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.81,0:36:13.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.92,0:36:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.05,0:36:16.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.68,0:36:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:24.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,飛行機？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.32,0:37:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.34,0:37:17.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,..すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.82,0:37:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it travels at five kilometers per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.88,0:37:20.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,時速5キロなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.51,0:37:21.45,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.28,0:37:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to the Minamitane launch facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.38,0:37:24.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,南種子の打ち上げ場まで
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.45,0:37:25.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there'll be a launch this year.\NFirst time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.85,0:37:28.69,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今年は久しぶりに打ち上げるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.79,0:37:32.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ　太陽系のずっと奥まで\N行くんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.08,0:37:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's supposed to go to the far reaches\Nof the solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.42,0:37:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many years it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.46,0:37:34.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何年もかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.44,0:37:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... you should really talk to Kanae\Nabout her plans for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.55,0:37:57.35,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんた　カナエの進路\Nちゃんと相談に乗ってやんなさいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.40,0:37:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how absent-minded she can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.45,0:37:59.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ぼんやりした子なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.10,0:38:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine. It's not like she's a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.12,0:38:02.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫よ　あの子も\Nもう子供じゃないんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.36,0:38:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I used to be just like that, a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.46,0:38:08.43,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も昔は　ああだったなぁ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.33,0:38:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that, Kabu? Tohno-kun apparently doesn't\Nknow what tomorrow will bring, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.43,0:38:14.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ　カブ　遠野くんも分からないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.52,0:38:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both the same. Tohno-kun and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.60,0:38:18.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒なんだ...遠野くんも
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.11,0:38:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must really be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.37,0:38:20.60,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それは本当に...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.91,0:38:24.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,想像を絶するくらい　孤独な旅であるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.95,0:38:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...a lonelier journey than anyone could imagine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.40,0:38:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To just press forward through\Nthe true pitch darkness...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.51,0:38:28.81,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本当の暗閣の中をただひたむきに
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.88,0:38:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Barely encountering even a single hydrogen atom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.92,0:38:32.58,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,1つの水素原子にさえ滅多に出会うことなく
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.22,0:38:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wholeheartedly believing\Nyou'll come closer to discovering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.22,0:38:38.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただただ　深淵にあるはずと信じる\N世界の秘密に近づきたいー心で
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.84,0:38:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the secrets of the universe\Nwithin the unfathomable abyss of space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.11,0:38:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how far we should go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.20,0:38:48.07,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,僕たちは　そうやって\Nどこまで行くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.34,0:38:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far CAN we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.47,0:38:51.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまで行けるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.05,0:39:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder when I got in the habit of\Nwriting messages to nobody?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.19,0:39:14.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出すあてのないメールを打つクセがついたのは\Nいつからだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.83,0:39:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanae, have you decided what you'll be doing in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.10,0:39:54.26,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カナエ　あんた　進路決めたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.30,0:39:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. Like I thought, I'm still not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.37,0:39:59.24,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん　やっぱりまだ分かんないけど　でもいいの決めたの！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.98,0:40:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right! I decided that\NI'll just take things on one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.44,0:40:03.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,1つずつ出来ることからやるの行ってくる！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.76,0:40:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.32,0:40:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since that day, a number of typhoons\Nhave passed through...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.46,0:40:24.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの日から　いくつかの台風が通りすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.50,0:40:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and the island's\Nbecome a little cooler each time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.70,0:40:28.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたびに島は少しずつす\Nずしくなっていった
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.11,0:40:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wind blowing through the sugarcane\Nhas taken on a slight chill...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.20,0:40:33.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,サトウキビを揺らす風が\Nかすかに冷気を孕み
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and the sky seems a little higher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.64,0:40:35.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,空がほんの少し高くなり
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.86,0:40:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The edges of the clouds have become gentler...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.98,0:40:38.31,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,雲の輪郭が優しくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.41,0:40:42.85,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,カブに乗る同級生たちが\N薄いシャンパーを羽織るようになった
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.41,0:40:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and my classmates have begun wearing light jackets\Nwhen riding their bikes with the change in the weather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.34,0:41:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By the time I managed to ride the waves again,\Nsix long months had passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.40,0:41:01.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私が半年ぶりに波の上に立てたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.77,0:41:06.07,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また夏がかろうじてのるそんな10月の半ばだった
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.81,0:41:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though it was the middle of October, it felt\Nlike a little bit of summer had been left behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.22,0:41:21.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本日夕方からの天候は晴れ\N最大風速は8mの予報となっています
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.33,0:41:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather forecast for tonight shows a clear evening\Nwith winds up to eight meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.99,0:41:25.08,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,佐々木さん　山田から告白されたらしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.52,0:41:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I heard that Yamada confessed to Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.28,0:41:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.29,0:41:27.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,さすがだなー
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.10,0:41:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Kanae, you seem awfully happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.19,0:41:29.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ？カナエ　なんか今日嬉しそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.61,0:41:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something good happen between you and Tohno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.80,0:41:31.63,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんとなんかあったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.99,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.07,0:41:33.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.58,0:41:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, I'm finally going to confess to Tohno-kun, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.60,0:41:37.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私だって今日こそ...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.04,0:41:40.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんに告白するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.83,0:41:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't tell him today, on the day\NI finally rode the waves again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.84,0:41:47.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,波に乗れた今日言わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.17,0:41:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sure I won't ever be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.21,0:41:50.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この先の　きっと...ずっと言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.59,0:42:01.49,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.65,0:42:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumida.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.59,0:42:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To-
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.79,0:42:02.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,と...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tohno-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.83,0:42:05.39,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くん...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.48,0:42:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,On your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.50,0:42:06.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今帰り？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.26,0:42:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.47,0:42:08.30,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.54,0:42:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.50,0:42:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.50,0:42:10.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ　一緒に帰ろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.14,0:42:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Sumida? Decided already today?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.16,0:42:35.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ　澄田　今日はもう決まり？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.78,0:42:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.87,0:42:48.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.89,0:42:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.05,0:42:57.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,...しくしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.12,0:42:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.48,0:42:58.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.17,0:43:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I'm sorry. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.69,0:43:04.16,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん...何でもないの
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.60,0:43:12.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,調子悪い？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.60,0:43:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your bike acting up?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.92,0:43:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... that's kind of weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.97,0:43:14.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　ヘンだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.33,0:43:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.34,0:43:17.17,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ダメ？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.22,0:43:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I think the spark plug's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.27,0:43:21.76,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん...プラグの寿命なんじゃないのかなこれお下がり？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.76,0:43:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this a hand-me-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.87,0:43:23.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん　お姉ちゃんの
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.06,0:43:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was Onee-chan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.21,0:43:24.90,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,加速で息継ぎしてなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.29,0:43:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it stall when you tried accelerating?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.01,0:43:26.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,してたかも
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.11,0:43:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It might have, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.56,0:43:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave it here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.68,0:43:32.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日はここに置かせてもらって\N後で家の人に取りにきてもらいなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.70,0:43:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have someone from your house pick it up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.12,0:43:33.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今日は歩こう
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.17,0:43:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's walk back today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.45,0:43:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'll walk by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.52,0:43:37.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ　私一人で歩くよ! \N遠野くんは先帰って
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.90,0:43:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.92,0:43:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're this far out, and your place is nearby, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.96,0:43:39.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここまできれば近いから
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.96,0:43:43.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それにちょっと...歩きたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.97,0:43:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I kind of want to walk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.06,0:44:19.29,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くん...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.14,0:44:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohno-kun, please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.60,0:44:20.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願い...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.94,0:44:32.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしたの！？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.94,0:44:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.98,0:44:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.05,0:44:36.41,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん　なんでもないの
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.82,0:44:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.41,0:44:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.52,0:44:37.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめんね...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.78,0:44:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumida...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:40.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,澄田...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.90,0:44:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm begging you... please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.96,0:44:45.55,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お願いだから...もう...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.66,0:44:46.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私に...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.71,0:44:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...don't be so nice to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.56,0:44:49.15,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やさしくしないで....！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.89,0:46:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As we humans desperately and recklessly\Nstretched our arms to the top of the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.06,0:46:27.96,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,必死に　ただ閣雲に空に手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.06,0:46:30.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんなに大きなカタマリを打ち上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.07,0:46:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and launched something\Nof that mass and size into the air...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.94,0:46:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...gazing off into the distance towards something\Nfar beyond our wildest dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.00,0:46:34.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気の遠くなるくらい　むこうにある何か見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.71,0:46:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I felt like I somewhat came to understand why\NTohno-kun was different from the other boys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.74,0:46:43.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんが他の人と\N違って見える理由が
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.38,0:46:45.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,少しだけ分かった気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.87,0:46:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And at the same time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.98,0:46:47.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そして　同時に
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.90,0:46:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I clearly realized that Tohno-kun\Nwasn't really looking at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.08,0:46:51.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんは私を見てなんて\Nいないんだということに
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.48,0:46:53.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私はハッキリと気づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.10,0:47:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which is why, on that day,\NI couldn't say a word to Tohno-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.16,0:47:02.75,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だからその日　私の遠野くんに\N何も言えなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.36,0:47:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohno-kun is really kind, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.54,0:47:18.98,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんは優しいけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.63,0:47:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's so truly kind, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.15,0:47:21.11,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とても優しいけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.25,0:47:23.31,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でもー
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.27,0:47:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Tohno-kun was always looking far beyond me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.42,0:47:25.01,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんはいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.12,0:47:29.78,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のずっとむこう...\Nもっとずっと遠くの何かを見ている
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.93,0:47:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Far beyond me, towards something in the distance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.43,0:47:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure I wouldn't be able to give Tohno-kun\Nwhat he truly desires.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.57,0:47:44.66,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私が遠野くんに望むことは\Nきっと叶わない
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.71,0:47:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But still... despite that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.77,0:47:46.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでも...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.64,0:47:49.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それでも私は遠野くんのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.23,0:47:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow, the day after, and even beyond that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.61,0:47:51.87,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと明日も明後日もその先も
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.84,0:47:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I know I'll still be helplessly in love with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.98,0:47:54.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱりどうしようもなく好きなんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.27,0:48:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While thinking solely of Tohno-kun,\NI cried myself to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.32,0:48:00.22,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,遠野くんのことだけを想いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.52,0:48:03.51,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きながら　私は眼った
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.48,0:49:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I strongly felt...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.54,0:49:31.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今　振り返れば
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.79,0:49:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that if I looked back now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.91,0:49:36.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとあの人振り返ると強く感じた
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.03,0:49:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...she would look back as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.35,0:49:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The last Chuo line train bound for Tokyo is now arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.49,0:49:53.93,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,中央.総武最終電車　東京行きが到着します
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.63,0:51:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay till New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.67,0:51:11.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お正月でいればいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.84,0:51:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but I have a million things to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.98,0:51:14.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん...でも色々準備もあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.91,0:51:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.05,0:51:18.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだな　彼にもうまいもの作ってやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.39,0:51:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to cook him good meals, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.61,0:51:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.32,0:51:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's ever a problem, don't hesitate to call us, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.55,0:51:22.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かあったら電話するのよ　アカリ
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.41,0:51:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.49,0:51:27.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫よ　来月には式で会うんだから\Nそんなに心配しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.75,0:51:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see each other at the wedding next month,\Nso don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.86,0:51:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better head home. It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.96,0:51:30.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,寒いからもう戻りなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.29,0:51:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last night, I dreamt of something from the distant past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.55,0:51:53.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆうべ　昔の夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.68,0:51:58.14,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も彼も　まだ子供だった
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.73,0:51:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back when he and I were both still children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.66,0:52:01.99,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと　昨日見つけた手紙のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.67,0:52:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure it's because of that letter I found yesterday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.63,0:52:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.75,0:52:56.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,水野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.39,0:52:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.78,0:52:57.64,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ　はい
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.53,0:52:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have time for that meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.75,0:52:58.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ミーテイングいいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.64,0:52:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.88,0:52:59.97,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.25,0:53:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through the act of living itself,\Nsadness piles up here and there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.36,0:53:13.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ　生活をしているだけで\N哀しみはそこここに積もる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.50,0:53:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether in the sheets hung to dry in the sun...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.80,0:53:18.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日に干したシーツにも\N洗面所の歯ブラシにも
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.43,0:53:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the single toothbrush in your bathroom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.66,0:53:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...or the history logs of your cell phone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.74,0:53:20.79,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,携帯電話の履歴にも
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.98,0:53:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Even now, I still love you... "{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.13,0:53:46.06,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたのことは今でも好きですと
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.12,0:53:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what the girl I'd been with for three years\Nsaid in that e-mail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.16,0:53:50.19,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,三年間付き合った女性はそうメールに書いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.17,0:53:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But I'm sure that even if we had written\N1,000 text messages back and forth... "{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.20,0:53:55.73,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも私たちはきっと\N1000回もメールをやりとりして
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.84,0:54:01.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,多分　心は1センチくらいしか\N近づけませんでした と
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.88,0:54:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"... our hearts probably wouldn't have moved\Neven 1 centimeter closer. "{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.69,0:54:12.05,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この数年間　とにかく前に進みたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.72,0:54:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over these past few years, I've only wanted to move\Nforward and touch that which I couldn't reach...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.16,0:54:17.02,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,届かないものに手を触れたくて\Nそれが具体的に何を指すのかも
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.79,0:54:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...though I've never been able to tangibly define what it was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.17,0:54:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not knowing where those obsessive thoughts\Ncame from, I simply continued to work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.53,0:54:20.33,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ほとんと脅迫的とも\N言えるようなその想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.43,0:54:24.56,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どこから湧いてくるのかも分からずに\N僕はただ働き続け
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.61,0:54:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then one day I realized that my heart was withering,\Nand in it there was nothing but pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.67,0:54:29.54,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気づけば日々弾力を失っていく心が\Nひたすら辛かった
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.00,0:54:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, one morning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.07,0:54:32.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そしてある朝
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.87,0:54:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...when I realized that I had completely lost my\Nearnest and acute feelings from long ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.91,0:54:35.94,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,かつてあれほどまでに真剣で切実だった思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.05,0:54:38.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,綺麗に失われてることに僕は気づき
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.27,0:54:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I knew I was at my limit...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.35,0:54:41.61,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう限界だと知ったとき
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.68,0:54:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and quit my job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.72,0:54:43.48,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,会社を辞めた
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.26,0:55:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yesterday, I had a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.38,0:55:11.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,昨日　夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.82,0:55:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream of long ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.02,0:55:14.25,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと昔の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.37,0:55:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Within the dream, the two of us were still thirteen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.48,0:55:18.32,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その夢の中では　僕たちはまだ13歳で
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.37,0:55:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...standing upon the vast field blanketed\Nin snow as far as the eye could see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.59,0:55:22.68,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そこは　一面の雪に覆われた広い田園で
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.75,0:55:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distance, the lights shimmering in\Nhouses were set sparsely, far and wide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.79,0:55:26.92,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,人家の灯りは　ずっと遠くにまばらに見えるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.03,0:55:32.37,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,振り積もる新雪には\N私たちの歩いてきた足跡しかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.12,0:55:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All that was left upon the newly fallen snow\Nwere our footprints.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.40,0:55:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.47,0:55:33.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうやって
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.87,0:55:37.36,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつかまた\N一緒に桜を見ることが出来ると
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.90,0:55:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we wished, without hesitation, that one day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.43,0:55:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the two of us would be able...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.47,0:55:40.88,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私も彼も　なんの迷いもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.22,0:55:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to see the cherry blossoms together again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.98,0:55:42.71,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.85,0:55:50.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつでも捜しているよ　どっかに君の姿を
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.13,0:55:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always searching for you,\Nalways searching for your figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.20,0:55:53.70,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向いのホーム　路地裏の窓
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.41,0:55:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,On the opposite platform,\Nor through window in the back alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.86,0:55:57.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなとこにいるはずもないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.09,0:55:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know you can't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.80,0:56:04.81,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願いがもしもかなうなら　今すぐ君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.86,0:56:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If my wish were to come true, I would be at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.82,0:56:08.40,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}できないことは　もう何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.08,0:56:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be nothing I couldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.42,0:56:14.81,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すべてかけてだきしめてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.67,0:56:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I would risk everything to embrace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.68,0:56:30.91,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}寂しさ紛らすだけなら　誰でもいいはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.81,0:56:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If only to avoid loneliness, anyone will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.18,0:56:38.18,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}星が落ちそうな夜だから　自分をいつわれない
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.42,0:56:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,On this night when it seem stars will fall\Nfrom the sky, I cannot lie to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.19,0:56:45.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One more time　季節よ　うつろわないで
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.35,0:56:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, don't fade away, seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.86,0:56:52.80,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One more time　ふざけあった時間よ
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.09,0:56:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, I want that time\Nwhen we fooled around together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.20,0:57:00.30,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつでも捜しているよ　どっかに君の姿を
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.48,0:57:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always searching for you,\Nalways searching for your figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.54,0:57:03.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}交差点でも　夢の中でも
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.81,0:57:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At the intersection, in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.15,0:57:07.52,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなとこにいるはずもないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.43,0:57:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know you can't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.91,0:57:15.07,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡はもしも起こるなら　今すぐ君に見せたい
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.23,0:57:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If miracles do happen, I want to show you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.13,0:57:18.57,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい朝　これからの僕
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.37,0:57:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the new dawn, who I'll be from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.72,0:57:24.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}言えなかった「好き」という言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.98,0:57:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the words "I love you" that I never said.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.98,0:57:40.00,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}夏の想い出がまわる
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.19,0:57:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The memories of summer revolve around me
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.89,0:57:47.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ふいに消えた鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.14,0:57:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and your throbbing heartbeat that suddenly stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.94,0:57:56.43,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつでも捜しているよ　どっかに君の姿を
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.15,0:57:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always searching for you,\Nalways searching for your figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.71,0:58:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In the city at dawn, in Sakuragi-cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.75,0:58:00.03,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明け方の街　桜木町で
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.25,0:58:03.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなとこに来るはずもないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.53,0:58:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know you can't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.08,0:58:11.10,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願いがもしもかなうなら　今すぐ君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.28,0:58:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If my wish were to come true, I would be at your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.25,0:58:14.72,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}できないことは　もう何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.56,0:58:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There would be nothing I couldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.84,0:58:18.42,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}すべてかけてだきしめてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.12,0:58:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I would risk everything to embrace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.64,0:58:25.67,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつでも捜しているよ　どっかに君の破片を
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.03,0:58:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always searching for you, always\Nsearching for even a fragment of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.79,0:58:29.27,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}旅先の店　新聞の隅
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.10,0:58:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At the shop I'm going to, in the corner of a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.40,0:58:32.82,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなとこにあるはずもないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.75,0:58:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know you can't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.15,0:58:40.21,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}奇跡はもしも起こるなら　今すぐ君に見せたい
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.56,0:58:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If miracles do happen, I want to show you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.23,0:58:43.77,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい朝　これからの僕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.61,0:58:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the new dawn, who I'll be from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.89,0:58:47.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}言えなかった「好き」という言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.27,0:58:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the words "I love you" that I never said.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.81,0:58:54.86,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつでも捜してしまう　どっかに君の笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.12,0:58:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I always end up looking somewhere for your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.07,0:58:58.46,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}急行待ちの　踏切あたり
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.37,0:58:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At the railroad crossing, waiting for the express to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.60,0:59:02.12,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなとこにいるはずもないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.05,0:59:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I know you can't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.29,0:59:09.47,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}命が繰り返すならば　何度も君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.60,0:59:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could live life over again,\NI would be at your side every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.70,0:59:13.38,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しいものなど　もう何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.09,0:59:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I would want nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.55,0:59:20.34,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君のほかに大切なものなど
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.93,0:59:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,more precious than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.77,1:02:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The End
